            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Honestly I am telling you, those who have given 5 stars to this shop are the staff people only. The school don't provide facilities as said on the day of admission. There receptionist is very rude and teachers are not bothering about students. They don't give so called discount on the tution fees if the student scores good marks in grade 10th BOARD Exam. Even there is a lot of communication gap b/w teachers and students. I have taught here in this school and my son have completed 12th this year from the same school. Even the working condition of teachers are also very pathetic that's why I left the school. There is a lack of discipline among teachers and so with students. Education is not good in this school. Here the coordinator find herself as if she is the VP. And also no change in the position of coordinators, since I joined the school till I left and my son, we found Ms. Surbhi Shrivastava only, who is quite jealous and revenge taking kind of teacher. She wants everyone (the parents, teachers, students, other staff members and even the seniors) to work under her. She is not a teacher, she is a politician. If you want to ruin your child's carrier just enroll your ward in this school.",
